causal_map:
Fourier transform → signal spectrum; 
                    signal spectrum → filter response; 
                    filter response → filtered signal spectrum; 
                    filtered signal spectrum → inverse Fourier transform → time-domain signal; 
                    time-varying filter H(t, s) → time-varying filter response; 
                    time-varying filter response → time-varying filtered signal; 
                    original signal → Fourier transform → filtered signal; 
                    time-varying filtered signal → inverse Fourier transform → final time-domain signal
